@vuejs I would not be surprised if there are other massive flaws in the rest of the tests.
@vuejs potentially, but If I have noticed this issues within minutes for 1 framework, I have severe concerns about general mis-information
@stefanpenner sure, would love to have a different, more objective test suite. That would benefit all framework authors.
@vuejs it has nothing really todo with TodoMVC itself but it does with the test suite.
@stefanpenner TodoMVC is not designed in favor of any particular framework, but of course you should take the results with a grain of salt.

@stefanpenner you are more than welcome to come up with a more natural test suite.
